N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 210.1 - Relocation payments governed by this part

State Regulations

Relocation payments to eligible persons for their moving
expenses caused by their displacement from real property acquired by the

Commissioner of Education shall be governed by the provisions of this

Part. Notes
